\prod_{i = 1}^{n} (2i - 1) =  \frac{(2n)!}{2^{n} n!}
 1\cdot 3 \cdot 5 \cdots (2n-1) = \frac{ 1 \cdot 2 \cdot 3 \cdot 4 \cdots (2n-1)\cdot (2n) }{2\cdot 4 \cdot 6 \cdots (2n)} 
